<subSubSection id="C37642ECFFC6FFF2FA105F835D4FF86D" pageId="43" pageNumber="595" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="8BD31167FFC6FFF2FA105F835D4FF86D" blockId="43.[1450,2657,1260,2122]" pageId="43" pageNumber="595">
<emphasis id="B918CD75FFC6FFF2FA105F835D6BF83F" bold="true" box="[1452,1802,1930,1963]" pageId="43" pageNumber="595">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Given the rarity and taxonomic uncertainty of the Dark Armored Tree-rat, it will not be possible to update this classification.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
